description: Try our easy to follow Reindeer Layered Mud Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Reindeer Layered Mud Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Just before serving, gently press on the mint eyes and carefully press in the skewers of the chocolate antlers on the top of the cake. Press on a strawberry lolly for the nose.
